#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Mae Grylli yn cynnwys cyfarwyddiadau adeiledig trwy'r ap i'ch helpu i "
"ffurfweddu a rheoli'ch sefydliad."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r dudalen hon yn darparu trosolwg o nodweddion allweddol a dolenni "
"uniongyrchol i ble gellir eu rheoli."

